item.p:
Vellum leaves, about 6 3/8 in. by 4 5/8, from a manuscript written in
                    three columns (e.g. fol. 8). These leaves are palimpsest (see Add. 17,135, upper text
                          ).

Vellum leaves, about 6 3/8 in. by 4 5/8, from another manuscript, written in two
                    columns. These leaves are palimpsest (see Add. 17,135, upper text
                          ).

Vellum leaves, about 6 3/8 in. by 4 5/8, from a manuscript of about the
                    viiith cent. They are palimpsest (see Add. 17,135, upper text
                          ).
